## Tech Stack

**Frontend:** React 19.x, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind CSS 4.x, Zustand
**Backend:** Node.js 22+, Hono 4.x, Drizzle ORM, PostgreSQL
**Infrastructure:** pnpm workspaces monorepo

## Commands

```bash
pnpm install              # Install dependencies
pnpm dev                  # Run all packages
pnpm --filter client dev  # Frontend only
pnpm --filter server dev  # Backend only
pnpm build                # Build
pnpm test                 # Testing
pnpm lint                 # Linting
pnpm --filter server db:migrate   # Run migrations
pnpm --filter server db:generate  # Generate migration from schema
```

